            "content": "<p>/1</p><p>Last Sunday was the hottest day on Earth in all recorded history, European climate agency reports<br /><a href=\"https://apnews.com/article/hottest-day-climate-change-heat-wave-warming-71e3e9d1fbfdc8503ef36eabec9390bd\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" translate=\"no\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://</span><span class=\"ellipsis\">apnews.com/article/hottest-day</span><span class=\"invisible\">-climate-change-heat-wave-warming-71e3e9d1fbfdc8503ef36eabec9390bd</span></a></p><p>2024-July-21 Was Earth\u2019s Hottest Day on Record<br />As of June 2024, the past 13 months have all been the hottest on record<br /><a href=\"https://truthout.org/articles/july-21-was-earths-hottest-day-on-record\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" translate=\"no\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://</span><span class=\"ellipsis\">truthout.org/articles/july-21-</span><span class=\"invisible\">was-earths-hottest-day-on-record</span></a></p><p><a href=\"https://mastodon.social/tags/ClimateChange\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"tag\">#<span>ClimateChange</span></a> <a href=\"https://mastodon.social/tags/Anthropogenic\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"tag\">#<span>Anthropogenic</span></a> <a href=\"https://mastodon.social/tags/GlobalWarming\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"tag\">#<span>GlobalWarming</span></a> <a href=\"https://mastodon.social/tags/FossilFuels\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"tag\">#<span>FossilFuels</span></a> <a href=\"https://mastodon.social/tags/capitalism\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"tag\">#<span>capitalism</span></a> <a href=\"https://mastodon.social/tags/billionaires\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"tag\">#<span>billionaires</span></a> <a href=\"https://mastodon.social/tags/Koch\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"tag\">#<span>Koch</span></a> <a href=\"https://mastodon.social/tags/ExxonMobil\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"tag\">#<span>ExxonMobil</span></a></p>",
